:name="Revision_Number" atidlm:value="" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/></atidlm:resourcepair></atidlm:link></citation> and substituting the following subsection:</text>
            <amend>
              <subprov skeleton="no" xml:lang="en-NZ">
                <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">1</label>
                <para xml:lang="en-NZ">
                  <text>A local authority must keep and maintain a rates record for each rating unit in its district that clearly shows—</text>
                  <label-para skeleton="no" xml:lang="en-NZ">
                    <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">a</label>
                    <para xml:lang="en-NZ">
                      <text>the amount of the ratepayer's liability for rates in respect of that unit; and</text>
                    </para>
                  </label-para>
                  <label-para skeleton="no" xml:lang="en-NZ">
                    <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">b</label>
                    <para xml:lang="en-NZ">
                      <text>any information required under <citation jurisdiction="nz">section 117K(2)</citation> that relates to the unit.</text>
                    </para>
                  </label-para>
                </para>
              </subprov>
            </amend>
          </para>
